  <!--Long description of the mod. Single line or multi line. Supports minimal markdown subset-->
  <LongDescription>
AdvancedTPM provides per-resource tax and production management with an AI-powered advisor and a detailed company browser. Key features include per-resource tax sliders, real-time production/consumption bars, category grouping, tax income tracking, and a company browser with efficiency and happiness indicators. The mod also includes an auto-tax engine with configurable rules and an adaptive learning advisor that records outcomes and recommends confidence-weighted adjustments.

For full feature details, screenshots and installation instructions, please see the project's README or edit the mod page on the hosting site.
  </LongDescription>
